Class Candidate

  • java.lang.Object
    • Candidate

  • public class Candidate
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Maygan Miguez Candidate class provides constructor method to construct a Candidate on a ballot using their name and affiliation. Provides methods for retrieving candidate's name, retrieving candidate's affiliation, incrementing vote count, retrieving total number of votes, and overrides toString method to return Candidate information. Created: Maygan Miguez, 28 February 2020, CMPS 1600 Lab section 2
